name: #4 CHAVIN DE HUANTAR
description:
The pre-Inca civilization of Chavin is historically known for being great shamans and healers under the teachings of the San Pedro cactus.(WACHUMA)
The stela of the bearer is an ancient stone monolith with a visual metaphorical message related to the acquisition of the attributes of animals by the members of the chavin cult. The cactus manages - due to its psychotropic action - to amplify the perception and mental faculties of the person who ingests it. Kawsaipak!
"ENTHEOGENS THROUGH TIMES" Collection
